Add a product by scanning it's barcode (note that the product might not be in the DB).

This app is a demo for ilustration only, not for commercial usage.
No transaction occure within this app!
The data (products) given in this app do not presume to ilustrate real pricing or names.

for barcode reading purposes the following library was used (thanks for your work!):
https://github.com/dm77/barcodescanner

this library and some others are Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0: http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0
